data.description: This is the home you've been waiting for! Highly sought after single-story, 4 bedroom, 2 bath in a quiet Newbury Park neighborhood. Nearly 2000 sq ft of living space, this home features a spacious sunken living room with vaulted ceiling, newer appliances, dual pane windows throughout, premium wood flooring, 11-year old roof. There is matching granite countertops in kitchen and bathrooms. Master bathroom is newly remodeled with deep tub and walk-in shower. The private backyard has a large covered patio and is lush with mature fruit trees, and a curly weeping willow tree adds a quaint southern charm.Home is close to schools, shopping and hiking/biking trails.
